Title: Knowledge Discovery by Accuracy Maximization
Description: A self-guided, weakly supervised learning algorithm for
        feature extraction from noisy and high-dimensional data. It
        facilitates the identification of patterns that reflect
        underlying group structures across all samples in a dataset.
        The method incorporates a novel strategy to integrate spatial
        information, improving the interpretability of results in
        spatially resolved data.
